{"id": "1460114591295209598", "channel_id": "1458369028706930802", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi! Sorry for the confusion.\nAfter double checking with our designers, Corposant's \"Pilot\" counts as a \"Buff\" card, as stated on the bottom of the card. \nWe will change this description to \"trigger when Buff Card, Symptom Card, or State Card\" is used to avoid future confusion.", "timestamp": "2026-01-12T03:34:06.182000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458369028706930802", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」\"Foreign Stamp Album\" effect does not match description", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1460211823013007433", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "Will put this as the final opinion, even just to make the team reflect on the future mechanics philosophy (if they have some comments on this, we would like to hear them out): \n\nThe Tentacle gathering is not a particularly fun mechanic to interact with for this reasons:\n- Is a never ending source of damage, removing the windows of opportunity to play more offensive or defensive depending on the enemy intentions.\n- Is fast ramping and you can't do nothing, in the majority of cases, to halt it.\n- It doesn't interact well with Counter, DR (that is already nerfed in Astral) or Barrier.\n- It encourage to kill the enemy as fast as possible, when the philosophy of Arc2 seems to push more for sustained DPS, with higher HP counts and the frequent implementation of Forgotten Embers\n\nNot all enemies are bad to fight, but some outliers, like Murphy, Gmurphy and maybe Chapter 4 last boss, but that is not the only problem that make it not too enjoyable to fight, could be revisited.", "timestamp": "2026-01-12T10:00:28.030000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
